'''塔什干－薩馬爾罕高速鐵路'''，又称'''阿弗拉西阿卜号'''，是一段長344公里的高速鐵路，其連接[[烏茲別克|烏茲別克]]兩大城：首都[[塔什干|塔什干]]與古都[[薩馬爾罕|薩馬爾罕]]。這條鐵路線沿線經過四個州，分別是[[塔什干州|塔什干州]]、[[錫爾河州|錫爾河州]]、[[吉扎克州|吉扎克州]]以及[[撒馬爾罕州|撒馬爾罕州]]。此鐵路線以撒马尔罕郊外的{{Link-uz|阿弗拉西阿卜遗址|Afrosiyob|阿夫拉西阿卜城址}}命名，終年运行。

== 歷史 ==
塔什干－薩馬爾罕高速鐵路自2011年3月11日開始動工，總工程預算為7,000萬美元。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://centralasianewswire.com/viewstory.aspx?id=3519 | title=Uzbekistan begins construction on high-speed railway | publisher=Central Asia Newswire | date=March 11, 2011 | accessdate=August 1, 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60clgvPz9?url=http://centralasianewswire.com/viewstory.aspx?id=3519 | archivedate=2011-08-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="can">{{cite web | url=http://centralasianewswire.com/International/Uzbekistanrsquos-high-speed-rail-plans-face-logistics-challenges/viewstory.aspx?id=2111 | title=Uzbekistan’s high-speed rail plans face logistics challenges | publisher=Central Asia Newswire | date=October 22, 2010 | accessdate=August 1, 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60clomigL?url=http://centralasianewswire.com/International/Uzbekistanrsquos-high-speed-rail-plans-face-logistics-challenges/viewstory.aspx?id=2111 | archivedate=2011-08-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>本鐵路線是以舊有[[在來線|在來線]]加以翻修並興建部分新軌道，使得全線得以現代化。<ref name="uzdaily">{{cite web | url=http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15111.htm | title=First high-speed Talgo electricity train arrives in Tashkent | publisher=Uzbekistan Daily | date=July 24, 2011 | accessdate=August 1, 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60cm9FzBg?url=http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15111.htm | archivedate=2011-08-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>除了連絡兩大城外，中途亦在次要的城鎮設立車站，例如：[[布哈拉|布哈拉]]以及[[希瓦_(烏茲別克斯坦)|希瓦]]，方便全鐵路沿線連絡。<ref name="can"/>這條長達344公里的高速鐵路，正常的列車營運速度為每小時250公里，因此連絡兩大城間的時間縮短為2小時。<ref name="uzdaily"/>全線在當時預計於2011年9月通車，<ref name="ri">{{cite web | url=http://www.railwayinsider.eu/wp/?p=22377 | title=Uzbekistan receives first high-speed train from Spain | publisher=Railway Insider | accessdate=August 1, 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60cmvi5Md?url=http://www.railwayinsider.eu/wp/?p=22377 | archivedate=2011-08-02 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>不過最終因某些因素而延遲通車計畫。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://centralasiaonline.com/en_GB/articles/caii/newsbriefs/2011/09/19/newsbrief-03 |title=Uzbekistan’s high-speed trains said to lack suitable tracks |accessdate=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2012-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120519161246/http://centralasiaonline.com/en_GB/articles/caii/newsbriefs/2011/09/19/newsbrief-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 營運現狀 ==
[[烏茲別克鐵路|烏茲別克鐵路管理部]]以3800萬歐元向[[西班牙|西班牙]][[塔爾高_(公司)|塔爾高車輛公司]]訂購高速鐵路車輛。<ref name="can"/><ref name="rg">{{cite web | url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/index.php?id=44&no_cache=1&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=13680&cHash=dca8f029fa | title=Talgo 250 arrives in Toshkent | publisher=Railway Gazette International | date=July 26, 2011 | accessdate=August 1, 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60cmUfRH8?url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/index.php?id=44 | archivedate=2011-08-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>首列訂購列車於2011年7月22日運抵烏國首都[[塔什干|塔什干]]。<ref name="rg"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15111.htm |title=First high-speed Talgo electricity train arrives in Tashkent, 24 July 2011  |access-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006080001/http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15111.htm |archive-date=2011-10-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>每列列車包含：兩節動力機電車輛以及八節車廂，每節車廂可以載運257名乘客。<ref name="rg"/>全線於2011年8月26日開始上線試運轉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15511.htm |title=Uzdaily: First high-speed electricity train carries out first trip from Samarkand and Tashkent, 27 August 2011  |accessdate=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2012-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111171755/http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15511.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.travelpulse.com/uzbekistan-launches-high-speed-tashkentsmarkand-rail-line.html |title=Uzbekistan Launches High Speed Tashkent-Smarkand Rail Line, September 08 2011 |access-date=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2012-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120602192327/http://www.travelpulse.com/uzbekistan-launches-high-speed-tashkentsmarkand-rail-line.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年10月8日，全線正式上線服務。初期營運每周兩個來回於[[塔什干|塔什干]]與[[薩馬爾罕|薩馬爾罕]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uzrailway.uz/rus.html?id=376 |title=ГАЖК «Ўзбекистон темир йўллари», ОАО «Узжелдоропасс» оъявляет, что началась продажа проездных документов на высокоскоростной поезд «Afrosiyob» |access-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008232743/http://uzrailway.uz/rus.html?id=376 |archive-date=2011-10-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15984.htm |title=High-speed Afrosiyob train starts to run between Tashkent and Samarkand, 6 October 2011 |access-date=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008081323/http://www.uzdaily.com/articles-id-15984.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>事實上，在初期運行的期間，路程時間是多於預期的，總共花費兩個半小時。<ref name=ab>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ut.uz/eng/business/25_hours_to_samarqand.mgr |title=Uzbekistan Today: 2.5 Hours to Samarqand |access-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120421131607/http://www.ut.uz/eng/business/25_hours_to_samarqand.mgr |archive-date=2012-04-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2012年2月，再有更多列車上線服務後，更改為每日一個來回班次，<ref>[http://uzdaily.com/articles-id-17417.htm High-speed train Afrosiyob to run seven times a week] {{Wayback|url=http://uzdaily.com/articles-id-17417.htm |date=20181003193043 }}. UzDaily.com. 13 February 2012</ref>總路程時間降低為兩小時又八分鐘。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gazeta.uz/2013/02/12/afrosiyob/|title=Поездка в Самарканд на поезде Afrosiyob теперь занимает два часа|publisher=Gazeta.uz|language=ru|accessdate=|date=2013-02-12|archive-date=2016-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508083136/https://www.gazeta.uz/2013/02/12/afrosiyob|dead-url=no}}</ref>

